:0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T12:47:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92bcc19033925bba5831350658e5692f538ec3d0","tid":368273,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T12:49:35.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺批評其他人唔關心政治/時事既人好撚ON9 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios \" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios </a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n回未呀OP <br />\n走場不要得<br />\n<br />\n順手回埋le部分<br />\n原文<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span> 係定義<br />\n好似叫<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人</span>係<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER</span>一樣<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前因</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">後果</span><br />\n<blockquote>不當類比<br />\nNIGGER=負面+黑人 黑人=黑人<br />\n但黑人一定=NIGGER NIGGER都一定=黑人<br />\n故此 黑人=黑人 NIGGER=黑人<br />\n所以無問題<br />\n你要PROOF 到無立場=負面 咪比你話無立場=港豬囉<br />\n港豬=無立場 但無立場唔一定係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人=NIGGER 係視乎講個個人咩心態<br />\n黑人係任何時候都可以=NIGGER<br />\n就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span><br />\n有主觀情感 呢個答案滿唔滿足到你<br />\n無立場係咪任何時候都係負面?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER(事實+負面)</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(事實+負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(事實+中性)</span><br />\n同<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬(事實+負面)</span><br />\n以上三者均是係<span style=\"color: red;\">事實</span>=事實+觀感<br />\n而例子1,2均係由洗手兄提出同接受<br />\n<br />\n而係以如此邏輯之下<br />\n洗手兄不斷要在下回答&quot;無立場係咪任何時候都係負面&quot;<br />\n一點可見 洗手兄本末倒置<br />\n將 負面 定性為 <span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span><br />\n嘅必要條件 而非 <span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span>嘅附加觀感<br />\n<br />\nLong story short<br />\nIf<br />\n無立場係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係Nigger<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係傻仔<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係中性 先可以話係智能障礙<br />\n<br />\n不過洗手兄又話<br />\n<blockquote>就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以無立場係咪任何時候都係負面 同無立場=港豬<br />\n係完全irrelevant </span>"},{"pid":"5925040b19ec335b2624603154d9824971919071","tid":368273,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T12:51:00.000Z","msg":"可以交配<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bda88aec504f7a6928272b05af88d8fceac3223","tid":368273,"uid":72676,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T12:51:22.000Z","msg":"由佢藍tick你開始點解樓主仲未意思到自己柒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce5b7f185bd9b8e13e0d7bd75ee3492a011fafb","tid":368273,"uid":27210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T12:51:54.000Z","msg":"大學生 金融業<br />\n含管 敦倫金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a2af6de7c358117094f30b61d1d776d09dc259","tid":368273,"uid":23485,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T12:53:05.000Z","msg":"柒到冇眼睇"},{"pid":"2690d39efafbd251c46ecbfeb9184242e824454e","tid":368273,"uid":4418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T12:58:07.000Z","msg":"條女心諗：「屌你老母你條毒撚FF以為拍緊愛情片咩？柒到唔想應你呀！」"},{"pid":"ac83dba60e4aa2fe8c753408e40c990a2ab87546","tid":368273,"uid":38934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T12:58:19.000Z","msg":"扑得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ecc8eb5499b5be7330ea961e18467f1c5a2d33","tid":368273,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T13:01:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扑得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真？"},{"pid":"a702068